- @title = "Embed out script on your site"

%h1 Embed our script

Insert this at the bottom of 
%b.tag &lt;body&gt; 
in your site:
%br
= text_field_tag 'jsinclude', "<script src='#{WIDGET_DOMAIN}widget/#{@site.id}' type='text/javascript'></script>", :class => 'code'

= button_to "Done", dashboard_account_path(current_account), :method => :get